# Build artifacts — regenerate with ./build.sh / go build
main.wasm
# Anchored so it only ignores the top-level `server` binary, NOT the
# cmd/server/ source dir (a bare `server` pattern matched both, which silently
# dropped cmd/server from the repo and broke the Docker build).
/server
cwp-server-bin

# Local Go build cache (serve.sh/build.sh default to /tmp, but ignore if set here)
/.gocache/
